{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"88dc8f5abe","title":"周恩来接见北京外语学院少数派师生谈话纪要","origin":"一九六六年北京化工学院《红色宣传员》战斗组、北京经济学院无产阶级革命团、北京市东方红印刷厂革命造反联络处、化工部化学工业出版社印刷厂联合汇编《无产阶级文化大革命参考资料（4）》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7288f5a7d3","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"88dc8f5abe"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"856207959d","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见北京外语学院少数派师生谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"ddd2065bad","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"5d7285ed92","type":"appellation","text":"〖总理接见外语学院的少数派代表，谈了该院两条路线斗争展览会的问题。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"f13c475891","type":"paragraph","text":"（关于展览会到外地展览）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"e505570571","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要提高一步，改进一下，可以出去。出去就要打响这一炮！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"7eedd5d3a6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要去看看这个展览会，然后再出去。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"4dab268085","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们学校党委检查了没有？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"cb00a05991","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：没有。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"be67ed15d1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我看你们就是对上面有兴趣，你们学校党委反而没事干了。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"f6b0c6164a","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：工作组利用过去的思想汇报或党团组织生活会上的汇报，拿来整人。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"360a363f99","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这是不健康的党风，这是王明搞的那一套，从苏联学来的。以后安子文也是这样，这是很不健康的党风，主席很反对。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"19250be3fb","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：有人不但汇报自己，还汇报别人。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"f62add42db","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这是全国很大的问题，一定要纠正。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"9d06423472","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们这些人代表多少组织？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"1105c1136c","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：七、八个。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"f470f0ab94","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：观点是否一致？","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"b78427031e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：一致。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"},{"id":"03361cd6ca","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么这么多，观点一致要少而精嘛！（谈到纠察队时）大学要什么纠察队，大家都是红卫兵嘛！纠察队好象是管红卫兵的，我建议取消。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe"}],"page":{"id":"5704c9b339","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88dc8f5abe","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}